{
  "stem": "13471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, [LAUGHS] the guy-- the Captain, Navy Captain, [? now force ?] driver, who had inspected the engineering spaces, he changed into dungarees in my quarters.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he crawled through-- they told me that he crawled through the bilges on his hands and knees tapping every rivet head.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Brother, did we get an inspection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- [LAUGHS] and so he came up onto the main deck to report to the Captain, the comm-- the admiral.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he put his arm or hand on my stack, I remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And by the way, my chief-- engineering room chief was behind him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he says, admiral, I have been engineering officer on these ships.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I've been commanding officer on these ships.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have been division officer on these ships.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's the best goddamn engine room I ever saw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, my chief was just going like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, proud as he could be.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- so anyway, they decided to fix us up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the chief couldn't take prosperity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That night, he went ashore, and he hung one on-- you couldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They-- shore patrol brought him back with a list, you know, this long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He'd taken over some striptease joint, and the stripteaser hadn't taken off enough.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he went up on the stage to help her take it off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] he got in a fight with a shore patrol.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he hit the-- blacked the shore patrol officer's eye.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I am telling you, I had a court martial on my-- I had a court martial.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was another story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But anyway, that's what I did in San Diego.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they-- they sent us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, we're going to repair you, but it'll be a low priority.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
